      <span class="shortdesc">How to create a folder for contributors to put content in.</span>

   <div class='screenshot'>
     <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M9/editors/create_folder.png" alt='Create folder screenshot'/> 
     <p>
      Creation of a <a href='../concepts/folder.html'>folder</a> with name `sar newspaper', 
      which is a folder for documents. 
     </p>
   </div>

   <p>
    In the <a href='./goto_content_browse_tab.html'>content browse tab</a>,
    in the tree view, click on 'Documents'. Then
    click on the selection menu at the top of the middle-right lane and select 'create folder'
    by clicking on it. A dialog window appears.
   </p>
   <p>
    Type a descriptive name for folder. 
   </p>

